# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:指在投資（例如買股票、炒樓）時，因為價格下跌而虧損，但已經買入嘅資產暫時唔會再跌，或者指將虧損嘅情況維持住，唔使再增加。
eng:to stop losing; to break even (in the context of investment)
<eg>
yue:呢隻股票跌咗好耐，但係今日突然反彈，終於止蝕咗。 (nei5 ze1 gou2 tou3 jat1 daai3 hou2 nei5, baaz3 ze1 gung1 daan1 fan3 ban3, zing1 ze1 zi2 zi6 sik1 ziu3.)
eng:The stock had been falling for a long time, but today it suddenly rebounded, finally stopping the losses. [end of text]


